_sText:
The anti-terror begin either in the arms factory, or in the post "CT". They can buy directly their weapons in the store, or then take a weapon of the arms factory or the post "CT". The terrorists begin in cells without weapons, except the knife. But 4 weapons are hidden there and 1 secret passage in 2 differentes cells... Other weapons and secret passages are presents in the map. 
As zones there is: 
- Cells 
- The arms factory 
- The post "CT" 
- The infirmary 
- The cage 
- The kitchen 
- The polling booth 
- The Mirador 
- The labyrinth 
- The soccer field 
- The swimming pool

Novelties : 
- Room of showers 
- Disco 
- Shooting range 
- A footbridge between mirador and the top of the swimming pool and another footbridge between the top of the swimming pool and the top of cells 
- A glass at the top of the mirador and the scout and the dual elite were deleted
- The secret passage of the polling booth was delected but other one was created
- A big secret passage between the room of showers, the polling booth and the cage
- Now, we can go out pipes by 3 other places
- All the traversables walls were replaced by real walls
- Weapons of the arms factory and the post "CT" have more ammunitions

- NOVELTIES : 
- New design for arms factory
- More ammunitions in weapons
- More weapons in the arms factory
- An awp is recoverable only by counter-terrorists above kitchen
- The shooting range was changed with distributors of weapons and a new trap !
- the conduit of the cage bring directly in the kitchen
- the glazed passage was deleted and the button to open the cage was moved more low
- the conduit of the polling booth was deleted, but the hidden button permit to open the door of the polling booth
- the conduit between the kitchen and the disco was deleted
- there is a new footbridge in the disco for counter-terrorists 
- there is a gun in the disco
- the ball of foot was changed and it rises higher
- there is a new footbridge in the soccer field for counter-terrorists
- the players do not cross any more furniture
- some weapons was deleted or changed in various conduits  
- the conduit between jails and arms factory was changed : only an access since the top of cells  
- some area was changed to counter-terrorists' area
- a break floor was created with two access for counter-terrorists and a footbridge around
- a weapon is hidden in the break floor
- buttons to open jails was changed
- personals textures was created
- The opening of polling booth and of the central cage was changed
- An new access for counter-terrorists in the disco was created
- (New order) : A three stairs was created without weapons and conduits
- (New order) : Several boxes was created between the central cage and the swimming pool without weapons and conduits. 

Have a good fun !

Video of presentation : 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CkW8xUFpuf0&feature=youtu.be

This map was originally made for a contest I took part in, I finished the part and decided to upload it here for you guys, the map is designed off Nova Prospekt from Halflife 2, I wanted to use  this idea as Nova Prospekt is seen as a high security prison that would be an ideal Jail theme.

It was designed for the Ct's to be able to have control over the t's as well as several routes for the t's to rebel.
The map is currently being played on the Edgegamers Jailbreak server and does not lag with 40 players on.
There are 20 Ct Spawns and 40 T Spawns, this version was created for Edgegamers, but different versions can be arranged if you notify me.

**This map requires NOBLOCK as many of the games are in small areas and you could end up with t's stuck together**

Features
* Climb
* Disco
* Maze
* Games Area
* Soccer
* Pool
* Heal
* Vents
* Execution rooms
* Cafeteria


Special Features
* A well designed Lockdown that locks each part of the prison down over a period of 3 minutes.


Minor Bugs
* Cubemap issues

The map is completely optimized and should not lag (tested with 40/40)

Ba_jail_electric_razor_v7, now called jb_razor_electric.  This is the beta release of the map.  I think the map will speak for itself.

-- August 13, 2009 --
Beta2 Released:

Changes include:
- Changed office bookcase to prop_static (doesn't move when you shoot it)
- Added a small library, garbage room, and laundry area in empty rooms
- Fixed the hidden T-buyzone (works properly now)
- Fixed pool teleport to make it less difficult to hit from the diving board
- Increased length of hidden ledge in kitchen to make it easier to get to sniper spot.

Fixes still needed:
- Shadow problem in infirmary (can see beds through the floor)
- Infirmary overhaul, needs to be made prettier. (too empty for my tastes).
